---
import PageHeading from "../components/page-heading.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="Documentation - Bangla Web Fonts">
  <div class="relative z-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto my-12 px-7 lg:px-0">
    <PageHeading
      title="Documentation"
      description="Bangla Web Fonts provides a collection of high-quality Bangla fonts that can be easily integrated into any website. Follow this guide to use any font from our collection efficiently."
    />

  <!-- Table of Contents -->
        <nav class="mt-10">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Table of Contents</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
                <li><a href="#introduction" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Introduction</a></li>
                <li><a href="#default" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">1. Using a Bangla Font (Default)</a></li>
                <li><a href="#minified" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">2. Using a Bangla Font (Minified Version)</a></li>
                <li><a href="#english-bangla" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">3. Using an English Font with a Bangla Font</a></li>
                <li><a href="#example" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">4. Full Example in HTML</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section id="introduction" class="mt-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Introduction</h2>
            <p class="mb-3">Bangla Web Fonts provides a collection of high-quality Bangla fonts that can be easily integrated into any website. Follow this guide to use any font from our collection efficiently.</p>
            <p>This example uses <strong>Solaiman Lipi</strong>, but many more fonts are available. To explore all available fonts, visit:  
                <a href="https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:underline">banglawebfonts.pages.dev</a>
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Default Version -->
        <section id="default" class="mt-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Using a Bangla Font (Default)</h2>
            <p>Include the following <code>&lt;link&gt;</code> tag inside the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> section of your HTML file:</p>
            <pre class="border border-gray-300 p-4 rounded-xl mt-3 overflow-auto text-sm scrollbar-hide"><code>&lt;link href="https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev/css/solaiman-lipi.css" rel="stylesheet"&gt;</code></pre>
            <p class="mt-3">Alternatively, use <code>@import</code> in CSS:</p>
            <pre class="border border-gray-300 p-4 rounded-xl mt-3 overflow-auto text-sm scrollbar-hide"><code>@import url('https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev/css/solaiman-lipi.css');</code></pre>
        </section>

        <!-- Minified Version -->
        <section id="minified" class="mt-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Using a Bangla Font (Minified Version)</h2>
            <p>For better page speed, use the minified version:</p>
            <pre class="border border-gray-300 p-4 rounded-xl mt-3 overflow-auto text-sm scrollbar-hide"><code>&lt;link href="https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev/css/solaiman-lipi.min.css" rel="stylesheet"&gt;</code></pre>
            <p class="mt-3">Or using <code>@import</code> in CSS:</p>
            <pre class="border border-gray-300 p-4 rounded-xl mt-3 overflow-auto text-sm scrollbar-hide"><code>@import url('https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev/css/solaiman-lipi.min.css');</code></pre>
        </section>

        <!-- English + Bangla Font -->
        <section id="english-bangla" class="mt-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Using an English Font with a Bangla Font</h2>
            <p>If you want to use an English font alongside a Bangla font, place the English font before the Bangla font in the <code>font-family</code> property.</p>
            <p class="mt-3">Example: Using "Playfair Display" for English and "Solaiman Lipi" for Bangla:</p>
            <pre class="border border-gray-300 p-4 rounded-xl mt-3 overflow-auto text-sm scrollbar-hide"><code>&lt;link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"&gt;
&lt;link href="https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev/css/solaiman-lipi.css" rel="stylesheet"&gt;</code></pre>
            <pre class="border border-gray-300 p-4 rounded-xl mt-3 overflow-auto text-sm scrollbar-hide"><code>body &#123;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Solaiman Lipi', serif;
&#125;</code></pre>
        </section>

        <!-- Full Example -->
        <section id="example" class="mt-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">4. Full Example in HTML</h2>
            <pre class="border border-gray-300 p-4 rounded-xl mt-3 overflow-auto text-sm scrollbar-hide"><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html lang="bn"&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
    &lt;meta charset="UTF-8"&gt;
    &lt;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;Bangla Web Font Example&lt;/title&gt;
    &lt;link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"&gt;
    &lt;link href="https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev/css/solaiman-lipi.css" rel="stylesheet"&gt;
    &lt;style&gt;
        body &#123;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Solaiman Lipi', serif;
        &#125;
    &lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;বাংলা ওয়েব ফন্ট ব্যবহার&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;This is an English sentence.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;এটি একটি বাংলা লেখা যা Solaiman Lipi ফন্ট ব্যবহার করে প্রদর্শিত হচ্ছে।&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre>
        </section>

  </div>
</Layout>
